ComicInfo.Summary:
Xena’s World Tour rolls on! Next stop…ROMANIA! Women and children are disappearing from a “haunted” village. Xena and Gabrielle must confront an Old God, one of malice and blood sacrifice, who craves a return to prominence, and will stop at nothing to gain new followers to carry out his awful bidding! By VITA AYALA (Black Panther, Shuri) and VASCO GEORGIEV!
